title: FULL SHOW: We React To The 2022 MTV VMA's, Nicki Minaj, & More

description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we discuss the 2022 Video Music Awards and all that went down. We happen to discuss Envy and Gia during the rumor report too! Listen to see why.... Charlamagne gives his Donkey of the day to thee "donkiest" state there is... any guesses?
